                               <br>  </p><p>The  Symposium <u>accepts  only original, unpublished work written in English</u>.  <u><strong>All  the papers</strong></u>  will be published by <strong>Springer  Verlag in </strong><strong>LNCS</strong><strong>.</strong>  We are soliciting three types of contributions: The <strong>FULL  (Research), PROJECT</strong>  (<strong>on-going  projects</strong>)  and <strong>SHORT  Papers</strong>  (<strong>Posters</strong>).  </p>
